<div style="background:var(--surface-2);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:48px 0;">
<div class="wrap">
  <p class="sec-eye">◆ Community Observations</p>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Weekly Analysis</h2>
  <div class="rule"></div>
  <div class="ana-grid">

    <div class="ana-block">
      <h3><span class="ana-icon">📊</span> Most-Mentioned Tickers</h3>
      <p>MAIN leads this week decisively with 7 mentions — the highest single-ticker count seen recently — cementing its role as the community's premier BDC holding. TRIN follows with 4 mentions, and PFFA rounds out the top three at 3, signaling continued interest in both direct lending and preferred stock income strategies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ana-block">
      <h3><span class="ana-icon">🏗️</span> Dominant Asset Classes</h3>
      <p>BDCs stand out this week with MAIN, TRIN, HTGC, CSWC, ARCC, and FSCO — a strong showing across internally and externally managed structures. Covered call ETFs remain well represented via MLPI, KSLV, GPIQ, USOY, NVII, SPYI, GPIX, CHPY, BTCI, NIHI, and KLIP. Infrastructure, preferred securities, and multi-sector credit CEFs round out the week's activity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ana-block">
